---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Rising Stars
description: Brand new repos with under 10 stars that deserve attention
---

<h1>Rising Stars</h1>
<p class="page-subtitle">Brand new repos with under 10 stars that deserve your attention. These projects are early — but someone saw potential.</p>

{% set risingEntries = collections.rising %}

{% if risingEntries.length > 0 %}
  <div class="rising-grid">
    {% for entry in risingEntries %}
      <article class="entry-card">
        <div class="entry-meta">
          <span class="signal-badge signal-{{ entry.data.signal }}">{{ entry.data.signal | signalEmoji }} rising</span>
          <span>{{ entry.data.date | dateReadable }}</span>
          <span>{{ entry.data.category }}</span>
        </div>
        <h3><a href="{{ entry.url }}">{{ entry.data.title }}</a></h3>
        {% if entry.data.stars is defined %}
          <span class="tag">{{ entry.data.stars }} stars</span>
        {% endif %}
        {% if entry.data.affects %}
          {% for tag in entry.data.affects %}
            <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        {% endif %}
        <p>{{ entry.data.description or entry.templateContent | striptags | truncate(200) }}</p>
        {% if entry.data.repo_url %}
          <a href="{{ entry.data.repo_url }}" class="repo-link">View on GitHub →</a>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
{% else %}
  <div class="empty-state">
    <p>No rising stars yet. Know a new repo that deserves attention?</p>
    <p>Run <code>/ai-radar contribute</code> or <a href="{{ site.repo }}/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">submit a PR</a> with a rising star entry.</p>
  </div>
{% endif %}

<style>
  .page-subtitle {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .rising-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .repo-link {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .empty-state code {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    padding: 0.2em 0.5em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
</style>
